data.description: Beautifully renovated 4 bedroom, 3 bath home in quiet neighborhood! Remodeled kitchen with newer stainless appliances, gas range, granite counters, farmhouse sink and cabinets!  Gorgeous 1st floor master bedroom with updated master bath & walk-in closet. Upgrades include remodeled baths, newer flooring, windows, encapsulated crawl space, wrapped roof trim, ceiling fans & paint! Relax in the large multi-purpose room or sunroom! Huge fenced backyard has concrete pad & side gate for RV or boat storage!  Easy commute to bases and close highway access.
